      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "このタイミングで、ターン……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And a turn right here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん、新曲の振り付け、なんとかなりそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ looks like the choreography for the new song is coming together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、芽衣と合わせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I have to coordinate it with Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遅いな、芽衣。もう練習開始の時間、過ぎてるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei’s late. It’s already past the beginning of practice time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、何かあったんじゃ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if something happened to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3600.0000000000014
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、お待たせ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan! Sorry for keeping you waiting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.666666599999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "芽衣、遅刻よ。心配させないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re late‚ Mei. You make me worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、早く着替えて……あれ、どうしてすずも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Get changed quickly… Oh‚ why is Suzu here too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "レッスンの前に聞いてほしいことがありますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s something we want you to hear before the lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "怜にとって大切なことですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s really important for you‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ダメ。レッスンが先",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope. The lesson comes first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "新ユニットのお披露目ライブまで時間がないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t have enough time before the launch concert for our new team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "期間限定のユニット活動だからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can’t put on an ungainly show‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "無様なライブは見せられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "just because this is temporary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ、すぐ着替えるから一言だけ聞いて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it. Just listen for a moment before I get changed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう、どうしたのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is this all about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに慌てて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you getting so worked up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜とお父様の話し合いの場を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We set up an opportunity for you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
